18#include "ODRSSReaderHelper.h"
19#include "ZXContainerAlgorithms.h"

21#include <array>

23namespace ZXing {
24namespace OneD {
25namespace RSS {
26
27static int combins(int n, int r)
28{
29 int maxDenom;
30 int minDenom;
31 if (n - r > r) {
32 minDenom = r;
33 maxDenom = n - r;
34 }
35 else {
36 minDenom = n - r;
37 maxDenom = r;
38 }
39 int val = 1;
40 int j = 1;
41 for (int i = n; i > maxDenom; i--) {
42 val *= i;
43 if (j <= minDenom) {
44 val /= j;
45 j++;
46 }
47 }
48 while (j <= minDenom) {
49 val /= j;
50 j++;
51 }
52 return val;
53}
54
55int
56ReaderHelper::GetRSSvalue(const std::array<int, 4>& widths, int maxWidth, bool noNarrow)
57{
58 int elements = Size(widths);
59 int n = Reduce(widths);
60 int val = 0;
61 int narrowMask = 0;
62 for (int bar = 0; bar < elements - 1; bar++) {
63 int elmWidth;
64 for (elmWidth = 1, narrowMask |= 1 << bar;
65 elmWidth < widths[bar];
66 elmWidth++, narrowMask &= ~(1 << bar)) {
67 int subVal = combins(n - elmWidth - 1, elements - bar - 2);
68 if (noNarrow && (narrowMask == 0) &&
69 (n - elmWidth - (elements - bar - 1) >= elements - bar - 1)) {
70 subVal -= combins(n - elmWidth - (elements - bar),
71 elements - bar - 2);
72 }
73 if (elements - bar - 1 > 1) {
74 int lessVal = 0;
75 for (int mxwElement = n - elmWidth - (elements - bar - 2);
76 mxwElement > maxWidth; mxwElement--) {
77 lessVal += combins(n - elmWidth - mxwElement - 1,
78 elements - bar - 3);
79 }
80 subVal -= lessVal * (elements - 1 - bar);
81 }
82 else if (n - elmWidth > maxWidth) {
83 subVal--;
84 }
85 val += subVal;
86 }
87 n -= elmWidth;
88 }
89 return val;
90}
